snippet.title: GMW Promo Video 2018
snippet.description: This is a (bit of a rambly) video of me inviting you to take part in Global Math Week 2018! It starts 10.10.2018 and by popular demand we're bringing back the wonders of EXPLODING DOTS! See www.globalmathproject.org
